{"source_id": "dm-ma-shihao", "source_type": "dm_user", "message_id": "om_x100b554e6b5db50ce114f92283e88c5", "chat_id": "ou_1e0851ad401d9abbc8619710ae0fcd28", "chat_type": "unknown", "sender_id": "ou_1e0851ad401d9abbc8619710ae0fcd28", "sender_name": "Ma Shihao", "direction": "incoming", "created_at": "2026-03-04 11:09", "content": "```SQL\nwith gpp as\n( select \n     *\n     ,id_number.hashed as id_number_hashed, '2026-03-02' as obs_date\n  from `p_mgr_id_mart.risk.detail_gtf_credit_application_tracking` ca\n  where ca.status='APPROVED' \n  qualify row_number() over(partition by user_id order by created_jkt_datetime desc)=1\n),\ngppm as\n( select \n     *\n  from\n  `p_mgr_id_mart.risk.detail_gtf_credit_application_tracking_ml`  \n  where status_name='APPROVED'\n  qualify row_number() over(partition by user_id order by created_jkt_datetime desc)=1)\n,temp as (\nselect \na.*,\ncase when b.user_id is not null then 'overlap' else 'not_olp' end as is_overlap\nfrom gpp a\nleft join gppm b on a.id_number.hashed=b.id_number_list.hashed_value\n)\n,\n\n```", "payload": {"content": "```SQL\nwith gpp as\n( select \n     *\n     ,id_number.hashed as id_number_hashed, '2026-03-02' as obs_date\n  from `p_mgr_id_mart.risk.detail_gtf_credit_application_tracking` ca\n  where ca.status='APPROVED' \n  qualify row_number() over(partition by user_id order by created_jkt_datetime desc)=1\n),\ngppm as\n( select \n     *\n  from\n  `p_mgr_id_mart.risk.detail_gtf_credit_application_tracking_ml`  \n  where status_name='APPROVED'\n  qualify row_number() over(partition by user_id order by created_jkt_datetime desc)=1)\n,temp as (\nselect \na.*,\ncase when b.user_id is not null then 'overlap' else 'not_olp' end as is_overlap\nfrom gpp a\nleft join gppm b on a.id_number.hashed=b.id_number_list.hashed_value\n)\n,\n\n```", "create_time": "2026-03-04 11:09", "deleted": false, "message_id": "om_x100b554e6b5db50ce114f92283e88c5", "msg_type": "post", "sender": {"id": "ou_1e0851ad401d9abbc8619710ae0fcd28", "id_type": "open_id", "name": "Ma Shihao", "sender_type": "user", "tenant_key": "1503d1037d07977c"}, "updated": false}}
